text: <!channel>  — Not sure when we're going to do it, but we have a few new folks in need of Biz Cards. I wanted to get a read on everybody's supply. If you're running low, please get in touch with me to let me know. Thanks.

<!channel> - Also, I was cleaning my desk a bit this morning. If anybody is interested in playing around with one of the Mio devices for awhile, please stop by. I have one here and you're welcome to use it, with the one caveat that you either make sure you take note of your experience with it (e.g. onboarding, ease of use, app, etc)
